Lift 2.4 and SBT 0.11.2 Basic Example Template

> git clone git@github.com:tuhlmann/lift_24_sbt11_selenium.git
> cd lift_24_sbt11_selenium
> ./sbt
> container:start

Your webapp is running on http://localhost:8080

The template also has support for:

- the sbt idea plugin (gen-idea)
- the sbt eclipse plugin
- JRebel (not scanning scanDirs)
- Jetty 7

This template integrates Selenium WebDriver with specs2 and a basic Lift project.

To run the tests type:

> ./sbt
> test
